If you're using Firefox, you could do something like this with your userContent.css[1]:<p><pre><code>  ::-moz-selection {
      color: #FFF !important;
      background-color: #00A /* or your color of choice */ !important;
  }
</code></pre>
[1] <a href="http://www-archive.mozilla.org/unix/customizing.html#usercss" rel="nofollow">http://www-archive.mozilla.org/unix/customizing.html#usercss</a>
